		text: "The qualities, specific traits, features or states of nouns like - big, attractive, silly, intelligent, fun, serious.",
	},
	
	{
		type: "paragraph",
		text: "They can also describe the quantity of nouns - many, few, some, hundreds, ten.",
	},
	
	{
		type: "paragraph",
		text: "The three articles used to discuss the specific or nonspecific - a, an, and the Colours and numbers - Purple, red, ten, hundred",
	},
	
	{
		type: "paragraph",
		text: "So, adjectives are basically descriptive words that describe or modify other words, making your writing and speaking much more specific, and a whole lot more interesting.",
